						<summary>

						<p>Much damaged. Seems to refer to the gift of land to the temple after excempting all the taxes. Besides, it also mentions Tāṉattā[r] the officer of the temple. Signatory Gurukularāyaṉ is mentioned. It also mentions in the fragmentary part II, a person named Māḷavamānikka Tirukkāṉappērudaiyaṉ.</p>						

